author: Lucia Suarez Sang
title: Wuhan, the Chinese city where coronavirus began, starts easing restrictions after two months of quarantine
description: The Chinese city where the coronavirus was first detected at the end of last year has begun to slowly re-open after more than two months under strict quarantine restrictions.
